name: MEV Capital WBTC
description: The WBTC vault curated by MEV Capital is focused on supplying liquidity to WBTC markets. It offers borrowers access to attractive rates through BTC LRTs incentives and provides suppliers with a competitive APR. Morpho Vaults are curated lending vaults that can allocate deposits to any number of Morpho Markets. Each vault is customizable and has a different risk profile. Curators are independent, third-party risk experts who use their expertise to offer various Morpho Vaults.
